1971;;Hands of the Ripper;;British;;Peter Sasdy;;Eric Porter, Angharad Rees;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hands_of_the_Ripper;;The infant daughter of Jack the Ripper is witness to the brutal murder of her mother by her father. Fifteen years later she is a troubled young woman who is seemingly possessed by the spirit of her late father. While in a trance she continues his murderous killing spree but has no recollection of the events afterwards. A sympathetic psychiatrist takes her in and is convinced he can cure her condition. However, he soon regrets his decision...